reviewText: Wished I could find the prior years.
great video, good price, fast shipping. Great deal.
Give to a 30 year old as a Christmas gift. They were very excited
My son loved this video...it would be nice to figure out how to get the other years..how to do this?

Entertaining video if you like the Ultimate Adventure series.  I thought this one was better than the 2006 one, but everybody has their own opinions.  If you are looking for a wheelin' video with rock music and half-naked chicks this is not the series for you.  But, if you are more interested in watching wheelin' footage and some dialogue this one will be fulfilling.
